V0411_01_00_00_0.text: I look forward to testing your strength!

V0411_01_00_01_0.text: Do not oppose me unless you wish to suffer!

V0411_01_00_02_0.text:
You look like a worthy foe.
Let's begin!

V0411_01_00_04_0.text: I knew we'd have to face each other someday, Kite.

V0411_01_00_04_1.text: I won't allow anyone to stop me - not even you!

V0411_01_00_05_0.text: It seems Kite isn't the only Duelist who has a Galaxy-Eyes.

V0411_01_00_06_0.text: I taught Kite everything he knows about Dueling.

V0411_01_00_06_1.text: Mizar, this will not be an easy fight!

V0411_03_00_00_0.text:
You can't win.
I know every move you're going to make.

V0411_03_00_01_0.text:
Are you done?
Then it's my turn.

V0411_03_00_04_0.text: I can see that you're a Duelist worth defeating.

V0411_03_00_05_0.text: This is still going exactly as I predicted.

V0411_05_00_00_0.text: I never give up on a Duel!

V0411_06_01_03_0.text: I expected you to do that.

V0411_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0411_07_09_01_0.text: I play the card I Set!

V0411_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0411_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0411_14_00_01_0.text: I can't know how a bell sounds until I strike it.

V0411_16_00_00_0.text: This will be my final act of kindness.

V0411_16_00_01_0.text: This will free you from all your suffering.

V0411_21_00_00_0.text:
What can you do?
You're like a bird who lost its wings.

V0411_21_00_01_0.text:
Have you looked at your LP?
This Duel is over.

V0411_21_00_02_0.text: With that, I end my turn.

V0411_21_00_03_0.text: It's still not the right time to make my move...

V0411_21_00_04_1.text: I refuse to give up, so give it your best shot!

V0411_28_00_00_0.text: I didn't even need to use my best cards.

V0411_28_00_01_0.text: We can have a rematch, but you'll never defeat me.

V0411_28_00_02_0.text: Your attacks aren't strong enough to succeed.

V0411_28_00_03_0.text: I knew every move you were going to make.

V0411_28_00_04_0.text: None of your strategies can fool me.

V0411_28_00_05_0.text: Kite, my Duel is far superior than you can imagine.

V0411_28_00_06_0.text: None of your tactics can surprise me.

V0411_28_00_06_1.text: After all, I'm the one who taught you how to Duel.

V0411_28_00_07_0.text: You are a noble Barian, but your time is over, Mizar!

V0411_28_00_08_0.text: I've analyzed all your Dueling data!

V0411_28_00_09_0.text: I taught you how to Duel better than this!

V0411_28_00_10_0.text:
You need to rest, Vetrix.
Think of your health.

V0411_29_00_01_0.text: I didn't know you were this talented.

V0411_29_00_03_0.text:
I knew you had one final trick.
Except I didn't know what.

V0411_29_00_04_0.text:
You were willing to lose a battle to win the war.
Well done.

V0411_29_00_05_0.text: I'm proud to see you've grown stronger.

V0411_29_00_05_1.text: I've always thought of you as family.

V0411_29_00_07_0.text: The strength of the Barian Emperors knows no bounds...

V0411_29_00_08_0.text:
You've seen what the Barians can do...
But keep fighting!

V0411_29_00_08_1.text:
Yuma... Kite...
I believe in you.

V0411_33_00_00_0.text: Whoever approaches me will be engulfed in flames!

V0411_33_00_01_0.text: It's finally time to make my move!

V0411_30_00_00_0.text: What!? You put that card in your deck?

V0411_30_00_01_0.text:
I don't just want to win.
I want to beat your best monster.

V0411_34_00_00_0.text: It's time for both of us to rest.

V0411_34_00_01_0.text: I sense that card has a powerful effect...

V0411_34_00_02_0.text:
Stand up!
The Duel isn't over!

V0411_34_00_03_0.text: A true Duelist keeps Dueling to the final LP.

V0411_34_00_04_0.text: If you're going to fail, it’s better you fail now.

V0411_34_00_05_0.text: But if you can survive, you will become a true Duelist!

V0411_34_00_06_0.text: Become the Duelist I know you are!

V0411_34_00_07_0.text: Good. That's what I was hoping for.

V0411_34_00_08_0.text: You're stalling until you can get your best monster back.

V0411_34_00_10_0.text: I won't let you get away with that!

V0411_34_00_11_0.text: It's not yet time to act...

V0411_34_00_12_0.text: Now's when I make my move!

V0411_35_00_01_0.text: It's not yet time to make my move.

V0411_36_00_00_0.text: Don't let victory slip from your grasp!

V0411_36_00_01_0.text:
Don't overdo it.
Just stall for time.

V0411_36_00_02_0.text:
What's wrong with you!
Be the Duelist I know you are!

V0411_36_00_04_0.text: Show me what you can do, Kite.

V0411_36_00_05_0.text:
What's wrong, Kite?
You can play better than this!

V0411_36_00_07_0.text: Don't push yourself too hard, Trey!

V0411_36_00_08_0.text: Now's the time to make your move, Quattro!

V0411_08_00_00_0.text: I activate Rank-Up-Magic Argent Chaos Force!

V0411_08_00_01_0.text: Argent Chaos Force's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0411_08_00_01_1.text: I add this card to my hand!

V0411_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Tannhauser Gate!

V0411_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Gravity Blaster!

V0411_08_00_04_0.text: Gravity Blaster's effect increases the monster's ATK!

V0411_08_00_05_0.text: I discard a card to activate the Spell Card, Cost Down!

V0411_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Monster Reborn!

V0411_08_00_07_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Terraforming!

V0411_08_00_07_1.text: I add a Field Spell in my deck to my hand!

V0411_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
World Legacy Monstrosity!

V0411_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Kuji-Kiri Curse!

V0411_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Mausoleum of the Emperor!

V0411_08_00_11_0.text: Mausoleum of the Emperor's effect activates!

V0411_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Limiter Removal!

V0411_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Machine Duplication!

V0411_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Blasting the Ruins!

V0411_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Bottomless Trap Hole!

V0411_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
B.E.F. Zelos!

V0411_08_00_17_0.text: B.E.F. Zelos's effect Special Summons a B.E.S. monster!

V0411_08_00_18_0.text: B.E.F. Zelos's effect places a counter on a B.E.S. monster!

V0411_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Boss Rush!

V0411_08_00_20_1.text: It Special Summons a B.E.S. monster from my deck!

V0411_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Shield Recovery!

V0411_08_00_22_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Kozmotown!

V0411_08_00_24_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Kozmo Lightsword!

V0411_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Kozmourning!

V0411_08_00_28_0.text: Kozmourning's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0411_09_00_00_1.text: For 1 Overlay Unit, it can attack you directly this turn!

V0411_09_00_01_0.text:
That attack won't reach me!
Dyson Sphere's effect activates!

V0411_09_00_01_1.text: When it has an Overlay Unit, it negates your attack once!

V0411_09_00_02_1.text: When attacked, it gains 2 Overlay Units from the Graveyard!

V0411_09_00_04_1.text: The monster it battled becomes its Overlay Unit.

V0411_09_00_05_0.text: Chaos Dyson Sphere has Dyson Sphere as its Overlay Unit!

V0411_09_00_05_1.text: So it can detach Overlay Units to deal you damage!

V0411_09_00_06_0.text: Arcjet Lightcraft's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0411_09_00_06_1.text: I revive a Machine from my Graveyard and make it Level 9!

V0411_09_00_07_0.text: Solar Wind Jammer's Level increases by 1 this Standby Phase.

V0411_09_00_08_0.text: I tribute Planet Pathfinder to get a Field Spell!

V0411_09_00_12_0.text: Summoning Crystal Core activates its effect!

V0411_09_00_14_0.text: Crystal Core's effect activates when it battles.

V0411_09_00_15_0.text: B.E.S. Tetran's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0411_09_00_16_0.text: When B.E.S. Tetran battles, it activates its effect.

V0411_09_00_17_0.text: I remove a counter to activate B.E.S. Tetran's effect!

V0411_09_00_18_0.text: Big Core's effect activates when it's successfully Summoned!

V0411_09_00_19_0.text: Big Core activates its effect when it battles.

V0411_09_00_20_0.text: Special Summoning Big Core MK-2 activates its effect!

V0411_09_00_21_0.text: Big Core MK-2's effect activates when it battles.

V0411_09_00_22_0.text: Big Core MK-3's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0411_09_00_23_0.text: When Big Core MK-3 battles, it activates its effect.

V0411_09_00_24_0.text: I banish Big Core MK-3 from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0411_09_00_25_0.text: Covered Core's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0411_09_00_26_0.text: Covered Core's effect activates when it battles.

V0411_09_00_27_0.text: Summoning Blaster Cannon Core activates its effect!

V0411_09_00_28_0.text: Blaster Cannon Core activates its effect when it battles.

V0411_09_00_29_0.text: By Summoning Sliprider, its effect activates!

V0411_09_00_30_0.text: When Sliprider is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0411_09_00_32_0.text: When Delta Shuttle is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0411_09_00_33_0.text: DOG Fighter activates its effect during this Standby Phase!

V0411_09_00_34_0.text: When DOG Fighter is destroyed, I can activate its effect!

V0411_09_00_35_0.text: When Landwalker is destroyed, I can activate its effect!

V0411_09_00_37_0.text: Dark Eclipser's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0411_09_00_38_0.text: When Dark Destroyer is Summoned, I can activate its effect!

V0411_09_00_39_0.text: When Dark Destroyer is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0411_09_00_41_0.text: Dark Planet activates its effect when it's destroyed!

V0411_09_00_43_0.text: Forerunner activates its effect when it's destroyed!

V0411_09_00_44_0.text: I banish Goodwitch to activate her effect!

V0411_09_00_45_0.text: I pay my LP to activate Goodwitch's effect!

V0411_09_00_46_0.text: I banish Soartroopers to activate its effect!

V0411_09_00_47_0.text: I pay my LP to activate Soartroopers's effect!

V0411_09_00_48_0.text: I banish Wickedwitch to activate her effect!

V0411_09_00_49_0.text: I pay my LP to activate Wickedwitch's effect!

V0411_09_00_50_0.text: I banish Farmgirl to activate her effect!

V0411_09_00_51_0.text: I pay my LP to activate Farmgirl's effect!

V0411_09_00_52_0.text: I banish Scaredy Lion to activate its effect!

V0411_09_00_53_0.text: I pay my LP to activate Scaredy Lion's effect!

V0411_09_00_54_0.text: I banish Tincan to activate its effect!

V0411_09_00_55_0.text: I pay my LP to activate Tincan's effect!

V0411_09_00_56_0.text: I banish Strawman to activate its effect!

V0411_09_00_57_0.text: I pay my LP to activate Strawman's effect!

V0411_09_00_58_0.text: I banish Dark Lady to activate her effect!

V0411_09_00_59_0.text: I pay my LP to activate Dark Lady's effect!

V0411_37_00_00_1.text: It's destiny for the earth to swallow the galaxy!

V0411_37_00_01_0.text: Appear above us and shine the light of victory!

V0411_37_00_02_1.text: The stars envelop all of creation to descend before me!

V0411_13_00_33_0.text: I Special Summon a DOG Fighter Token!

V0411_19_00_29_0.text:
Scaredy Lion!
Muster the courage to attack!
